og</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/1993/09/17/api-gateway-with-lambda/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/1993/09/17/api-gateway-with-lambda.png" type="image/png" length="19678" /> </item> <item> <title>Access S3, DynamoDB with Lambda</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AWS</category> <description>S3 객체 생성 이벤트로 Lambda를 트리거해 파일을 처리하고 DynamoDB에 적재, test event로 반복 검증한 실습</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/1993/09/17/access-s3-dynamodb-with-lambda/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/1993/09/17/access-s3-dynamodb-with-lambda/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/1993/09/17/access-s3-dynamodb-with-lambda.png" type="image/png" length="23967" /> </item> <item> <title>Failover for HA</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Database</category> <description>Orchestrator GUI로 MySQL 마스터 장애 시 자동 페일오버를 Docker 컨테이너로 구성하고 인위적 다운으로 승격·복구까지 실습한 기록</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/1993/09/17/failover-for-ha/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/1993/09/17/failover-for-ha/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/1993/09/17/failover-for-ha.png" type="image/png" length="16646" /> </item> <item> <title>S3 object encryption</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AWS</category> <description>S3의 SSE-S3·SSE-C·SSE-KMS·DSSE-KMS 네 방식 차이와 업로드 CLI 옵션, SSE-KMS boto3 up/download 코드까지 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/1993/09/17/s3-object-encryption/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/1993/09/17/s3-object-encryption/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/1993/09/17/s3-object-encryption.png" type="image/png" length="19225" /> </item> <item> <title>VPC Endpoint with Role</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AWS</category> <description>Bastion Host로 프라이빗 웹 서버에 접속하고 Gateway Endpoint와 IAM Role로 S3·DynamoDB에 게이트웨이 없이 접근하는 실습</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/1993/09/17/vpc-endpoint-with-role/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/1993/09/17/vpc-endpoint-with-role/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/1993/09/17/vpc-endpoint-with-role.png" type="image/png" length="19917" /> </item> <item> <title>AI Gateway 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AI</category> <description>AI Gateway가 토큰 단위로 LLM 트래픽을 통제하는 원리와 LiteLLM·Kong·Portkey·Cloudflare·Envoy 5종 비교, 가드레일 설계까지 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/ai-gateway-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/ai-gateway-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/ai-gateway-정리.png" type="image/png" length="18003" /> </item> <item> <title>LiteLLM으로 AI Gateway 구축과 운영</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AI</category> <description>LiteLLM Proxy와 Ollama 로컬 모델로 게이트웨이를 세워 라우팅·폴백·캐시 히트·예산 차단·프로메테우스 관측까지 응답 헤더로 실측한 기록</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/litellm%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-ai-gateway-%EA%B5%AC%EC%B6%95%EA%B3%BC-%EC%9A%B4%EC%98%81/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/litellm%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-ai-gateway-%EA%B5%AC%EC%B6%95%EA%B3%BC-%EC%9A%B4%EC%98%81/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/litellm으로-ai-gateway-구축과-운영.png" type="image/png" length="17621" /> </item> <item> <title>AWS ALB Pre-Warming 지원 종료</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AWS</category> <description>2025년 종료되는 ALB Pre-Warming을 대체하는 LCU-R 예약 방식과 값 추산법, 두 방식의 비용·설정 차이를 표로 비교</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/19/aws-alb-pre-warming-%EC%A7%80%EC%9B%90-%EC%A2%85%EB%A3%8C/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/19/aws-alb-pre-warming-%EC%A7%80%EC%9B%90-%EC%A2%85%EB%A3%8C/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2025/03/19/aws-alb-pre-warming-지원-종료.png" type="image/png" length="19646" /> </item> <item> <title>CDN과 동적콘텐츠 통합 시 차이점</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AWS</category> <description>CloudFront와 ALB를 함께 쓸 때 성능·보안·비용·캐싱 차이를 표로 비교하고 동적 콘텐츠 캐싱 시 Cache-Control 주의점을 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/19/cdn%EA%B3%BC-%EB%8F%99%EC%A0%81%EC%BD%98%ED%85%90%EC%B8%A0-%ED%86%B5%ED%95%A9-%EC%8B%9C-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/19/cdn%EA%B3%BC-%EB%8F%99%EC%A0%81%EC%BD%98%ED%85%90%EC%B8%A0-%ED%86%B5%ED%95%A9-%EC%8B%9C-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2025/03/19/cdn과-동적콘텐츠-통합-시-차이점.png" type="image/png" length="13241" /> </item> <item> <title>rsync로 EBS 복제하는 방법</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AWS</category> <description>rsync로 EBS 볼륨을 다른 EBS로 복제해 용량 축소·파일시스템 변경에 쓰는 절차, -axcHAWS·numeric-ids 옵션까지 기록</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2024/02/18/rsync%EB%A1%9C-ebs-%EB%B3%B5%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2024/02/18/rsync%EB%A1%9C-ebs-%EB%B3%B5%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2024/02/18/rsync로-ebs-복제하는-방법.png" type="image/png" length="16740" /> </item> <item> <title>CORS 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Network</category> <description>CORS 에러가 나는 5가지 시나리오를 원인·해결로 나누고 Access-Control 계열 응답 헤더 역할을 표로 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/12/cors-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/12/cors-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2025/03/12/cors-정리.png" type="image/png" length="14594" /> </item> <item> <title>DB 로그와 Aurora 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Database</category> <description>WAL·Redo·Undo·Binlog 등 DB 로그 종류와 MySQL·PostgreSQL 차이, Aurora가 로그를 공유 스토리지에서 다루는 방식까지 비교</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/10/db-%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%99%80-aurora-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/10/db-%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%99%80-aurora-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2025/03/10/db-로그와-aurora-정리.png" type="image/png" length="16722" /> </item> <item> <title>DDoS 유형별 대응 방법 요약</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Security</category> <description>HTTP Flooding·SYN·DNS 증폭 등 DDoS 유형을 OSI 계층별로 나눠 Nginx·iptables·커널 파라미터 대응 설정을 표로 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/19/ddos-%EC%9C%A0%ED%98%95%EB%B3%84-%EB%8C%80%EC%9D%91-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/19/ddos-%EC%9C%A0%ED%98%95%EB%B3%84-%EB%8C%80%EC%9D%91-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2025/03/19/ddos-유형별-대응-방법-요약.png" type="image/png" length="14940" /> </item> <item> <title>eBPF 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Linux</category> <description>eBPF의 verifier·JIT·maps·CO-RE 구조와 커널 모듈과의 차이, 훅 위치·개발 스택·Cilium·Falco 같은 대표 제품까지 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/ebpf-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/ebpf-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/ebpf-정리.png" type="image/png" length="14190" /> </item> <item> <title>bpftrace와 Cilium으로 eBPF 실습</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Linux</category> <description>bpftrace와 Cilium으로 커널 추적과 서비스 네트워킹을 실측하고 strace 대비 이벤트당 약 2600배 낮은 오버헤드를 수치로 비교한 기록</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/bpftrace%EC%99%80-cilium%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-ebpf-%EC%8B%A4%EC%8A%B5/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/bpftrace%EC%99%80-cilium%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-ebpf-%EC%8B%A4%EC%8A%B5/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/bpftrace와-cilium으로-ebpf-실습.png" type="image/png" length="17873" /> </item> <item> <title>서버 부팅 방식 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Linux</category> <description>MBR·GPT·UEFI·GRUB·ESP 개념과 AWS EC2 Xen·Nitro 세대에서 /boot/efi 없이 부팅되는 이유를 세대·OS별로 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/10/%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EB%B6%80%ED%8C%85-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/10/%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EB%B6%80%ED%8C%85-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2025/03/10/서버-부팅-방식-정리.png" type="image/png" length="13588" /> </item> <item> <title>EDNS 란</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Network</category> <description>EDNS가 OPT 레코드로 DNS를 확장하는 방식과 2019 DNS Flag Day 영향, 사용·미사용 시 패킷 크기·DNSSEC 차이를 비교</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/18/edns-%EB%9E%80/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/18/edns-%EB%9E%80/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2025/03/18/edns-란.png" type="image/png" length="14138" /> </item> <item> <title>Private EKS Cluster 트러블슈팅 내역[Draft]</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Kubernetes</category> <description>Private EKS 클러스터에서 마주친 CoreDNS hosts 수정·OCSP·PKIX·self-signed 인증서 오류 대응을 모은 트러블슈팅 기록</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/11/private-eks-cluster-%ED%8A%B8%EB%9F%AC%EB%B8%94%EC%8A%88%ED%8C%85-%EB%82%B4%EC%97%ADdraft/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/11/private-eks-cluster-%ED%8A%B8%EB%9F%AC%EB%B8%94%EC%8A%88%ED%8C%85-%EB%82%B4%EC%97%ADdraft/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2025/03/11/private-eks-cluster-트러블슈팅-내역draft.png" type="image/png" length="21778" /> </item> <item> <title>Storage 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Linux</category> <description>RAID 0~10과 LVM 조합, 오브젝트·블록 스토리지, EXT4·XFS·ZFS 파일시스템, Inode, Instance Store와 EBS를 표로 비교한 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/10/storage-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:08:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2025/03/10/storage-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2025/03/10/storage-정리.png" type="image/png" length="17804" /> </item> </channel> </rss>